  POST /recorder/save-generated-test - Save AI generated test
  POST /recorder/save-test-case - Save recorded test to disk
  GET  /recorder/sessions   - List active sessions
  GET  /recorder/saved-tests - List all saved recorder test cases
  GET  /recorder/test/<id>  - Get saved test with full details (actions)

